data.title: Did Saladin have any descendants? If so, what happened to them and why were they not rulers after him in Egypt or Syria?
data.meta_description: Answer (1 of 2): Saladin did indeed have descendants, but they did not play significant roles as rulers in Egypt or Syria after him. Saladin, also known as Salah ad-Din, was a prominent figure in Islamic history, particularly renowned for his role in the Crusades and his establishment of the Ayyu...
